review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2020
name: J.Mahoney
title: Pumpkin flavor no good this time around
review: I used to LOVE noosa pumpkin. Was a nice little treat for fall. This year it was just gross. Wayyy too sweet. More sugar than spiced. They only got the extra star because I got two and ate around the pumpkin in the second one and the yogurt was unaffected.

review: I liked that it was not overly sweet but that does not mean it lacked flavor.This is good.I was sorry to finish it.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2020
name: JH
title: Love noosa and limited edition flavor
review: Get it while you can. Noosa is more of a dessert for me than a primary yogurt go to since it leans on the sweet side.The pumpkin flavor is not overbearing. Really enjoy most of the flavors that Noosa offers.

review: I wish I could get this flavor year round.It's pumpkin-y without being overwhelming.It's pumpkin, not pumpkin spice.So yum.
